## 9. Feature Module Template: Trade

```
Sources/TradeFeature/
├── TradeView.swift                    // SwiftUI view
├── TradeViewModel.swift               // @Observable, injected dependencies
├── Components/
│   ├── OrderBookView.swift            // Order book UI component
│   ├── PriceHeaderView.swift          // Price display with change %
│   └── ChartContainerView.swift       // WebView chart wrapper
├── TradeCoordinator.swift             // Protocol (navigation contract)
└── Internal/
    └── OrderBookCalculator.swift      // Pure function: order book merging logic

Tests/TradeFeatureTests/
├── TradeViewModelTests.swift
├── OrderBookCalculatorTests.swift
└── Mocks/
    ├── MockTradeCoordinator.swift
    └── MockGetAllowedInstrumentsUseCase.swift
```

**File sizing:** TradeView ~150 lines, TradeViewModel ~200 lines, OrderBookCalculator ~80 lines. The current 650-line TradeViewModel gets split: order book logic moves to a pure calculator, navigation moves to coordinator, WebSocket subscription management moves to use cases.

